'''Dynamic Synergetics, Inc. (DSI)''' was a subsidiary of the [[InterGalactic Banking Clan/Legends|InterGalactic Banking Clan]] that operated a [[DSI Hyperbaride Synthesis Plant|hyperbaride synthesis plant]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Marca/Legends|Marca]]. The company was nationalized by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

